# Same State is a bring-your-own-key demo — the browser holds the user's
# OpenRouter key for the session and forwards it through /api/openrouter/*.
# Nothing here is required for a working local deploy.
#
# Optional: pin the HAPI base URL. Defaults to https://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4
# if unset. Override for a private FHIR test server (e.g. Synthea + HAPI
# in a container).
# HAPI_BASE_URL=https://hapi.fhir.org/baseR4

# Optional: attach a fallback OpenRouter key so callers without a key can
# run the demo. WARNING: this key will be charged for every request
# against your instance. Leave unset for the safe default (no fallback).
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY_FALLBACK=
